newHome.location:
Located directly across from the Gateway Shopping Centre in Knocknacarra, these houses provide a large and spacious accommodation, finished to the highest standard with a BER rating of A3.

Bothar Stiofán is a stone’s throw from the Gateway shopping centre (B&Q, Dunnes Stores, Next, New Look, Pharmacy etc), within easy access of local schools, sporting facilities, church, post office etc., just 4 km from the city centre and 2 km to Salthill proper with all its amenities and facilities to include the Salthill Promenade, Galway Golf Club, Leisureland Centre, many local shops, bars, cafés and restaurants.
